c: 2
v: 272
t: "Kutungamirwa kwavo hakubvi kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)), asi Allah vanotungamira uyo wavanoda. Uye chipi zvacho chamunoita chakanaka ndechenyu, uye hamupi kunze kwekuti muchitsvaga mufaro hwaAllah (kuonana navo). Uye chipi zvacho chamunopa chakanaka, muchapuhwa muripo zvizere musina kudzvanyirirwa"